File-Tree

Dustperados/
├── .github/                       # GitHub specific configurations (e.g., workflows)
│   └── workflows/
│       └── release.yml
├── css/                           # All CSS files for your system
│   ├── dustperados.css            # Main system stylesheet
│   └── forms.css                  # Styles for forms (e.g., input fields)
│   └── lib/                       # Third-party CSS libraries (if any)
├── fonts/                         # Custom fonts for your system (if any)
├── img/                           # Images used by your system (icons, backgrounds)
│   ├── actors/                    # Actor-specific images (e.g., default token image)
│   ├── items/                     # Item-specific images
│   └── system/                    # General system images
├── lang/                          # Localization files for different languages
│   └── en.json                    # English translations for your system strings
├── module/                        # All JavaScript modules for your system
│   ├── dustperados.js             # Main system entry point (initializes everything)
│   ├── config.js                  # System-wide configuration (e.g., global constants, actor types)
│   ├── settings.js                # Game settings registration
│   ├── templates.js               # Handlebars template preloading
│   ├── chat.js                    # Logic for chat messages and roll cards
│   ├── dice.js                    # Custom dice rolling logic or dice definitions
│   ├── documents/                 # Custom Document classes (for V10+ systems)
│   │   ├── actor.js               # Custom Actor Document class
│   │   └── item.js                # Custom Item Document class
│   └── sheets/                    # JavaScript classes for custom sheets
│       ├── sheets.js              # Central file to register all custom sheets
│       ├── dustperados-actor-sheet.js # Your custom Actor sheet class
│       └── dustperados-item-sheet.js  # Your custom Item sheet class
├── packs/                         # Compendium packs for items, actors, journal entries, etc.
│   ├── items.db                   # Database for common items
│   ├── abilities.db               # Database for pre-defined abilities (if you have them)
│   └── spells.db                  # Database for spells (if applicable)
├── templates/                     # Handlebars HTML templates for sheets, chat cards, etc.
│   ├── actor/                     # Actor sheet templates
│   │   ├── dustperados-actor-sheet.html # Main actor sheet HTML template
│   │   └── parts/                 # Partial templates for reuse within actor sheet
│   │       ├── actor-header.html
│   │       └── actor-abilities.html # A partial for your abilities section
│   ├── item/                      # Item sheet templates
│   │   └── dustperados-item-sheet.html
│   └── chat/                      # Chat card templates
│       └── roll-card.html
├── system.json                    # Your system's manifest file
├── template.json                  # Data model definitions for actors, items (if used)
├── README.md                      # Your system's README file
└── .gitignore                     # Files and folders to ignore in Git
